Requirements
This project uses the following Python libraries:

🔹 Flask
A lightweight web framework used to build the backend API.

Handles HTTP requests (/send, /queue)
Serves JSON responses
Runs the core application server

🔹 Flask-CORS
Used to enable Cross-Origin Resource Sharing.

Allows frontend (browser) to communicate with backend API
Required when frontend and backend run on different ports or domains
Prevents CORS errors in browser

🔹 boto3
AWS SDK for Python used to interact with AWS services.

Sends messages to Amazon SQS
Retrieves queue size
Used in both:
app.py (API)
worker.py (background worker)

🔹botocore
Low-level dependency of boto3.
Handles request signing and AWS API communication
Installed automatically but pinned here for stability